text: "These Days" is a 1999 song by Brian Kennedy featuring Ronan Keating. It was taken from Kennedy's studio album Now That I Know What I Want and went to number 4 in Ireland. ==Track listing== CD single # "These Days" - 4:04 # "I'll Be Waiting" - 3:28 # "Under Irish Stars" - 3:56 # "Interview with Brian Kennedy and Ronan Keating" - 3:29 ==References== Category:1999 songs Category:Ronan Keating songs
title: These Days (Brian Kennedy song)
